snippet.title: Celebrities React To Being Arrested At Brett Kavanaugh Protest in D.C.
snippet.description:
Amy Schumer, Emily Ratajkowski, Amber Heard Stand Up And Protest Against Brett Kavanaugh For Surpreme Court.
Subscribe: https://goo.gl/Hnoaw3
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Presented by Saphia
https://www.instagram.com/saphiahall/
https://twitter.com/saphiahall

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Other Videos you might like:

10 Celebrities Who Stood Up To Bullying
https://youtu.be/PREoC3QuipA

25 Things Kylie Jenner Spends Her Millions On
https://youtu.be/jqRtGKLMufU

Many women and men were in the U.S. capital on Thursday protesting the possible appointment of Brett Kavanaugh to the Supreme Court, after many allegations against him. Among these women were some of your favorite celebrities including Amy Schumer, Emily Ratajkowski, and Amber Heard. Take a look at how these celebs reacted to being questioned by the police, and arrested for standing up for what they believe to be right. Let us know what you think in the comments below about all of this controversy!
